Father, Fifth Brother, and Sixth Brother home.

162
00:15:08,850 --> 00:15:10,570
Third Master,

163
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:13,820
it has been hard on you.

164
00:15:25,270 --> 00:15:28,230
Welcome Commander, Fifth Master

165
