271
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:56,470
You say that the days passed really fast.

272
00:25:56,470 --> 00:26:00,970
In the blink of an eye, I've already been married to the Xiao family for 20 years.

273
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:05,440
I know all those madams

274
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:09,090
